<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Multimedia Player</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Multimedia Player</h1>
    <section>
      <h2>Now Playing: Sailing Away</h2>
      <audio 
      controls
      aria-label="Introduction video about map method">
      <source
      type="audio/mp3"
      src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/js-music-player/sailing-away.mp3">
      </audio>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What is a map method and how does it work?</h2>
      <video 
      width="640"
      controls>

      <source
      type="video/mp4"
      src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/what-is-the-map-method-and-how-does-it-work.mp4">
      <track
      kind="captions"
      srclang="en"
      label="English"
      src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/what-is-the-map-method-and-how-does-it-work.vtt">
     </video>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Transcript</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin aliquet neque at eleifend tristique. Donec eget erat quis ipsum aliquet bibendum. Nulla quis euismod quam, eget semper ante. Phasellus purus metus, blandit sed ornare quis, maximus eget augue. </p>
    </section>
</body>

</html>
